PrecisEnactment of the CHEQUE HOLDING POLICY DISCLOSURE (BANKS) REGULATIONS which provide that banks must disclose - in writing - their policy concerning the holding of funds when a customer opens a personal deposit account, or when the bank changes its cheque-holding policy.
